{
  "video_id": "HiwJ0hNl1Fw",
  "title": "Let's design social media that drives real change | Wael Ghonim",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13142.0,
      "end_time": 14315.0,
      "text": "I once said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14849.0,
      "end_time": 17483.0,
      "text": "\"If you want to liberate a society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17507.0,
      "end_time": 19523.0,
      "text": "all you need is the Internet.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20261.0,
      "end_time": 21415.0,
      "text": "I was wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22121.0,
      "end_time": 24701.0,
      "text": "I said those words back in 2011,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 24725.0,
      "end_time": 27647.0,
      "text": "when a Facebook page I anonymously created"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27671.0,
      "end_time": 29986.0,
      "text": "helped spark the Egyptian revolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30724.0,
      "end_time": 35304.0,
      "text": "The Arab Spring revealed social media&#39;s greatest potential,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35328.0,
      "end_time": 39336.0,
      "text": "but it also exposed its greatest shortcomings."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40300.0,
      "end_time": 44220.0,
      "text": "The same tool that united us to topple dictators"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 45550.0,
      "end_time": 47229.0,
      "text": "eventually tore us apart."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 48229.0,
      "end_time": 53123.0,
      "text": "I would like to share my own experience in using social media for activism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 53148.0,
      "end_time": 56679.0,
      "text": "and talk about some of the challenges I have personally faced"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 56703.0,
      "end_time": 58528.0,
      "text": "and what we could do about them."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 59818.0,
      "end_time": 61580.0,
      "text": "In the early 2000s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 62334.0,
      "end_time": 64219.0,
      "text": "Arabs were flooding the web."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 65619.0,
      "end_time": 68580.0,
      "text": "Thirsty for knowledge, for opportunities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 68604.0,
      "end_time": 72316.0,
      "text": "for connecting with the rest of the people around the globe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 72340.0,
      "end_time": 76270.0,
      "text": "we escaped our frustrating political realities"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 76735.0,
      "end_time": 80699.0,
      "text": "and lived a virtual, alternative life."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 81684.0,
      "end_time": 86260.0,
      "text": "Just like many of them, I was completely apolitical until 2009."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 86835.0,
      "end_time": 90344.0,
      "text": "At the time, when I logged into social media,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 90368.0,
      "end_time": 92887.0,
      "text": "I started seeing more and more Egyptians"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 92912.0,
      "end_time": 95657.0,
      "text": "aspiring for political change in the country."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 96244.0,
      "end_time": 98894.0,
      "text": "It felt like I was not alone."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 100577.0,
      "end_time": 102283.0,
      "text": "In June 2010,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 102308.0,
      "end_time": 105712.0,
      "text": "Internet changed my life forever."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 107550.0,
      "end_time": 109532.0,
      "text": "While browsing Facebook,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 110263.0,
      "end_time": 114815.0,
      "text": "I saw a photo, a terrifying photo, of a tortured, dead body"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 115493.0,
      "end_time": 117372.0,
      "text": "of a young Egyptian guy."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 117891.0,
      "end_time": 120160.0,
      "text": "His name was Khaled Said."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 121800.0,
      "end_time": 126361.0,
      "text": "Khaled was a 29-year-old Alexandrian who was killed by police."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 127990.0,
      "end_time": 129120.0,
      "text": "I saw myself in his picture."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 129924.0,
      "end_time": 132400.0,
      "text": "I thought, \"I could be Khaled.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 132853.0,
      "end_time": 136923.0,
      "text": "I could not sleep that night, and I decided to do something."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 137542.0,
      "end_time": 140430.0,
      "text": "I anonymously created a Facebook page"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 140670.0,
      "end_time": 143407.0,
      "text": "and called it \"We are all Khaled Said.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 144645.0,
      "end_time": 149270.0,
      "text": "In just three days, the page had over 100,000 people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 149294.0,
      "end_time": 152898.0,
      "text": "fellow Egyptians who shared the same concern."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 153390.0,
      "end_time": 155790.0,
      "text": "Whatever was happening had to stop."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 156631.0,
      "end_time": 159401.0,
      "text": "I recruited my co-admin, AbdelRahman Mansour."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 160590.0,
      "end_time": 162932.0,
      "text": "We worked together for hours and hours."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 162956.0,
      "end_time": 165884.0,
      "text": "We were crowdsourcing ideas from the people."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 165908.0,
      "end_time": 167351.0,
      "text": "We were engaging them."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 167376.0,
      "end_time": 169940.0,
      "text": "We were calling collectively for actions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 169964.0,
      "end_time": 173859.0,
      "text": "and sharing news that the regime did not want Egyptians to know."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 174733.0,
      "end_time": 177697.0,
      "text": "The page became the most followed page"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 177721.0,
      "end_time": 179124.0,
      "text": "in the Arab world."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 179148.0,
      "end_time": 183502.0,
      "text": "It had more fans than established media organizations"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 183526.0,
      "end_time": 185301.0,
      "text": "and even top celebrities."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 186468.0,
      "end_time": 188935.0,
      "text": "On January 14, 2011,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 189555.0,
      "end_time": 192880.0,
      "text": "Ben Ali fled out of Tunisia"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 192112.0,
      "end_time": 194866.0,
      "text": "after mounting protests against his regime."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 195589.0,
      "end_time": 197462.0,
      "text": "I saw a spark of hope."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 198144.0,
      "end_time": 201326.0,
      "text": "Egyptians on social media were wondering,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 201350.0,
      "end_time": 203691.0,
      "text": "\"If Tunisia did it, why can&#39;t we?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 204715.0,
      "end_time": 206907.0,
      "text": "I posted an event on Facebook and called it"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 206931.0,
      "end_time": 211738.0,
      "text": "\"A Revolution against Corruption, Injustice and Dictatorship.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 212635.0,
      "end_time": 217142.0,
      "text": "I posed a question to the 300,000 users of the page at the time:"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 217685.0,
      "end_time": 220301.0,
      "text": "\"Today is the 14th of January."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 220969.0,
      "end_time": 224220.0,
      "text": "The 25th of January is Police Day."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 224580.0,
      "end_time": 226259.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a national holiday."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 226283.0,
      "end_time": 230226.0,
      "text": "If 100,000 of us take to the streets of Cairo,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 230251.0,
      "end_time": 232600.0,
      "text": "no one is going to stop us."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 232300.0,
      "end_time": 233802.0,
      "text": "I wonder if we could do it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 234797.0,
      "end_time": 239279.0,
      "text": "In just a few days, the invitation reached over a million people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 239303.0,
      "end_time": 243330.0,
      "text": "and over 100,000 people confirmed attendance."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 243562.0,
      "end_time": 245903.0,
      "text": "Social media was crucial for this campaign."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 246329.0,
      "end_time": 249531.0,
      "text": "It helped a decentralized movement arise."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 249999.0,
      "end_time": 252499.0,
      "text": "It made people realize that they were not alone."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 252927.0,
      "end_time": 255753.0,
      "text": "And it made it impossible for the regime to stop it."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 256259.0,
      "end_time": 259500.0,
      "text": "At the time, they didn&#39;t even understand it."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 259656.0,
      "end_time": 265889.0,
      "text": "And on January 25th, Egyptians flooded the streets of Cairo and other cities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 265913.0,
      "end_time": 267887.0,
      "text": "calling for change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 267911.0,
      "end_time": 270206.0,
      "text": "breaking the barrier of fear"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 270230.0,
      "end_time": 272129.0,
      "text": "and announcing a new era."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 273947.0,
      "end_time": 275552.0,
      "text": "Then came the consequences."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 276592.0,
      "end_time": 281371.0,
      "text": "A few hours before the regime cut off the Internet and telecommunications,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 281395.0,
      "end_time": 285342.0,
      "text": "I was walking in a dark street in Cairo, around midnight."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 286750.0,
      "end_time": 289340.0,
      "text": "I had just tweeted, \"Pray for Egypt."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 289423.0,
      "end_time": 292529.0,
      "text": "The government must be planning a massacre tomorrow.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 293587.0,
      "end_time": 295835.0,
      "text": "I was hit hard on my head."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 296589.0,
      "end_time": 298699.0,
      "text": "I lost my balance and fell down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 298723.0,
      "end_time": 302223.0,
      "text": "to find four armed men surrounding me."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 302698.0,
      "end_time": 305918.0,
      "text": "One covered my mouth and the others paralyzed me."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 306711.0,
      "end_time": 309796.0,
      "text": "I knew I was being kidnapped by state security."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 310701.0,
      "end_time": 312930.0,
      "text": "I found myself in a cell,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 314259.0,
      "end_time": 316389.0,
      "text": "handcuffed, blindfolded."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 317270.0,
      "end_time": 318251.0,
      "text": "I was terrified."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 318615.0,
      "end_time": 319939.0,
      "text": "So was my family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 320956.0,
      "end_time": 322581.0,
      "text": "who started looking for me"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 322605.0,
      "end_time": 325512.0,
      "text": "in hospitals, police stations and even morgues."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 326569.0,
      "end_time": 327840.0,
      "text": "After my disappearance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 327864.0,
      "end_time": 331253.0,
      "text": "a few of my fellow colleagues who knew I was the admin of the page"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 331277.0,
      "end_time": 335476.0,
      "text": "told the media about my connection with that page,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 335500.0,
      "end_time": 338422.0,
      "text": "and that I was likely arrested by state security."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 339189.0,
      "end_time": 343572.0,
      "text": "My colleagues at Google started a search campaign trying to find me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 343596.0,
      "end_time": 347578.0,
      "text": "and the fellow protesters in the square demanded my release."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 348880.0,
      "end_time": 350540.0,
      "text": "After 11 days of complete darkness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 350564.0,
      "end_time": 351784.0,
      "text": "I was set free."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 352516.0,
      "end_time": 354128.0,
      "text": "And three days later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 354152.0,
      "end_time": 356714.0,
      "text": "Mubarak was forced to step down."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 357505.0,
      "end_time": 361649.0,
      "text": "It was the most inspiring and empowering moment of my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 362633.0,
      "end_time": 364224.0,
      "text": "It was a time of great hope."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 365265.0,
      "end_time": 368914.0,
      "text": "Egyptians lived a utopia for 18 days during the revolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 369685.0,
      "end_time": 371557.0,
      "text": "They all shared the belief"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 371581.0,
      "end_time": 375873.0,
      "text": "that we could actually live together despite our differences,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 375897.0,
      "end_time": 378353.0,
      "text": "that Egypt after Mubarak would be for all."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 379267.0,
      "end_time": 380514.0,
      "text": "But unfortunately,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 380538.0,
      "end_time": 384973.0,
      "text": "the post-revolution events were like a punch in the gut."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 386609.0,
      "end_time": 387988.0,
      "text": "The euphoria faded,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 388775.0,
      "end_time": 390662.0,
      "text": "we failed to build consensus,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 391840.0,
      "end_time": 395250.0,
      "text": "and the political struggle led to intense polarization."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 395813.0,
      "end_time": 398602.0,
      "text": "Social media only amplified that state,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 398626.0,
      "end_time": 402294.0,
      "text": "by facilitating the spread of misinformation, rumors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 402803.0,
      "end_time": 405165.0,
      "text": "echo chambers and hate speech."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 405189.0,
      "end_time": 407549.0,
      "text": "The environment was purely toxic."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 408265.0,
      "end_time": 414378.0,
      "text": "My online world became a battleground filled with trolls, lies, hate speech."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 415660.0,
      "end_time": 418329.0,
      "text": "I started to worry about the safety of my family."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 419655.0,
      "end_time": 422320.0,
      "text": "But of course, this wasn&#39;t just about me."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 423145.0,
      "end_time": 427515.0,
      "text": "The polarization reached its peak between the two main powers --"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 428930.0,
      "end_time": 430327.0,
      "text": "the army supporters and the Islamists."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 430986.0,
      "end_time": 433394.0,
      "text": "People in the center, like me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 433418.0,
      "end_time": 435118.0,
      "text": "started feeling helpless."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 436587.0,
      "end_time": 439870.0,
      "text": "Both groups wanted you to side with them;"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 439111.0,
      "end_time": 441361.0,
      "text": "you were either with them or against them."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 442737.0,
      "end_time": 444639.0,
      "text": "And on the 3rd of July 2013,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 444663.0,
      "end_time": 449170.0,
      "text": "the army ousted Egypt&#39;s first democratically elected president,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 449194.0,
      "end_time": 453765.0,
      "text": "after three days of popular protest that demanded his resignation."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 454519.0,
      "end_time": 457214.0,
      "text": "That day I made a very hard decision."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 457688.0,
      "end_time": 461534.0,
      "text": "I decided to go silent, completely silent."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 462106.0,
      "end_time": 463775.0,
      "text": "It was a moment of defeat."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 465101.0,
      "end_time": 467905.0,
      "text": "I stayed silent for more than two years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 467929.0,
      "end_time": 470830.0,
      "text": "and I used the time to reflect on everything that happened,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 471394.0,
      "end_time": 473881.0,
      "text": "trying to understand why did it happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 474773.0,
      "end_time": 476218.0,
      "text": "It became clear to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 476242.0,
      "end_time": 481163.0,
      "text": "that while it&#39;s true that polarization is primarily driven"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 481187.0,
      "end_time": 483220.0,
      "text": "by our human behavior,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 483460.0,
      "end_time": 487490.0,
      "text": "social media shapes this behavior and magnifies its impact."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 488315.0,
      "end_time": 491406.0,
      "text": "Say you want to say something that is not based on a fact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 491430.0,
      "end_time": 494142.0,
      "text": "pick a fight or ignore someone that you don&#39;t like."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 494914.0,
      "end_time": 497621.0,
      "text": "These are all natural human impulses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 497645.0,
      "end_time": 499799.0,
      "text": "but because of technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 499824.0,
      "end_time": 503248.0,
      "text": "acting on these impulses is only one click away."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 504562.0,
      "end_time": 507505.0,
      "text": "In my view, there are five critical challenges"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 507529.0,
      "end_time": 509847.0,
      "text": "facing today&#39;s social media."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 510794.0,
      "end_time": 513891.0,
      "text": "First, we don&#39;t know how to deal with rumors."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 514493.00000000006,
      "end_time": 517219.00000000006,
      "text": "Rumors that confirm people&#39;s biases"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 517243.00000000006,
      "end_time": 521320.00000000006,
      "text": "are now believed and spread among millions of people."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 522590.00000000006,
      "end_time": 526400.0,
      "text": "Second, we create our own echo chambers."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 526595.0,
      "end_time": 529912.0,
      "text": "We tend to only communicate with people that we agree with,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 529936.0,
      "end_time": 532100.0,
      "text": "and thanks to social media,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 532124.0,
      "end_time": 536725.0,
      "text": "we can mute, un-follow and block everybody else."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 538247.0,
      "end_time": 543670.0,
      "text": "Third, online discussions quickly descend into angry mobs."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 543571.0,
      "end_time": 545258.0,
      "text": "All of us probably know that."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 545833.0,
      "end_time": 547627.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s as if we forget"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 547651.0,
      "end_time": 550911.0,
      "text": "that the people behind screens are actually real people"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 550935.0,
      "end_time": 552449.0,
      "text": "and not just avatars."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 553254.0,
      "end_time": 557636.0,
      "text": "And fourth, it became really hard to change our opinions."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 558309.0,
      "end_time": 561593.0,
      "text": "Because of the speed and brevity of social media,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 561617.0,
      "end_time": 564550.0,
      "text": "we are forced to jump to conclusions"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 564575.0,
      "end_time": 567639.0,
      "text": "and write sharp opinions in 140 characters"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 567663.0,
      "end_time": 569847.0,
      "text": "about complex world affairs."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 570402.0,
      "end_time": 574252.0,
      "text": "And once we do that, it lives forever on the Internet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 574276.0,
      "end_time": 577378.0,
      "text": "and we are less motivated to change these views,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 577403.0,
      "end_time": 579434.0,
      "text": "even when new evidence arises."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 580330.0,
      "end_time": 583590.0,
      "text": "Fifth -- and in my point of view, this is the most critical --"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 584246.0,
      "end_time": 588550.0,
      "text": "today, our social media experiences are designed in a way"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 588574.0,
      "end_time": 591511.0,
      "text": "that favors broadcasting over engagements,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 591535.0,
      "end_time": 593554.0,
      "text": "posts over discussions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 594586.0,
      "end_time": 597258.0,
      "text": "shallow comments over deep conversations."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 597764.0,
      "end_time": 601814.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s as if we agreed that we are here to talk at each other"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 601838.0,
      "end_time": 604930.0,
      "text": "instead of talking with each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 605244.0,
      "end_time": 607680.0,
      "text": "I witnessed how these critical challenges contributed"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 607704.0,
      "end_time": 611160.0,
      "text": "to an already polarized Egyptian society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 611410.0,
      "end_time": 613154.0,
      "text": "but this is not just about Egypt."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 613601.0,
      "end_time": 616803.0,
      "text": "Polarization is on the rise in the whole world."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 617325.0,
      "end_time": 619899.0,
      "text": "We need to work hard on figuring out"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 619923.0,
      "end_time": 623244.0,
      "text": "how technology could be part of the solution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 623268.0,
      "end_time": 625278.0,
      "text": "rather than part of the problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 627720.0,
      "end_time": 630412.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a lot of debate today on how to combat online harassment"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 630436.0,
      "end_time": 631658.0,
      "text": "and fight trolls."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 631992.0,
      "end_time": 633459.0,
      "text": "This is so important."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 633818.0,
      "end_time": 635670.0,
      "text": "No one could argue against that."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 636251.0,
      "end_time": 641468.0,
      "text": "But we need to also think about how to design social media experiences"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 641492.0,
      "end_time": 644670.0,
      "text": "that promote civility and reward thoughtfulness."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 645512.0,
      "end_time": 646882.0,
      "text": "I know for a fact"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 646906.0,
      "end_time": 650122.0,
      "text": "if I write a post that is more sensational,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 650146.0,
      "end_time": 653656.0,
      "text": "more one-sided, sometimes angry and aggressive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 653681.0,
      "end_time": 656452.0,
      "text": "I get to have more people see that post."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 656791.0,
      "end_time": 658480.0,
      "text": "I will get more attention."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 659726.0,
      "end_time": 661990.0,
      "text": "But what if we put more focus on quality?"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 663149.0,
      "end_time": 664374.0,
      "text": "What is more important:"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 664398.0,
      "end_time": 667510.0,
      "text": "the total number of readers of a post you write,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 667750.0,
      "end_time": 671696.0,
      "text": "or who are the people who have impact that read what you write?"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 672846.0,
      "end_time": 677212.0,
      "text": "Couldn&#39;t we just give people more incentives to engage in conversations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 677236.0,
      "end_time": 679903.0,
      "text": "rather than just broadcasting opinions all the time?"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 680788.0,
      "end_time": 682186.0,
      "text": "Or reward people for reading"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 682210.0,
      "end_time": 684566.0,
      "text": "and responding to views that they disagree with?"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 686820.0,
      "end_time": 690795.0,
      "text": "And also, make it socially acceptable that we change our minds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 690819.0,
      "end_time": 692511.0,
      "text": "or probably even reward that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 693343.0,
      "end_time": 697492.0,
      "text": "What if we have a matrix that says how many people changed their minds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 697516.0,
      "end_time": 700671.0,
      "text": "and that becomes part of our social media experience?"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 701206.0,
      "end_time": 704283.0,
      "text": "If I could track how many people are changing their minds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 704307.0,
      "end_time": 708800.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d probably write more thoughtfully, trying to do that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 708320.0,
      "end_time": 711737.0,
      "text": "rather than appealing to the people who already agree with me"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 711761.0,
      "end_time": 714322.0,
      "text": "and \"liking\" because I just confirmed their biases."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 715512.0,
      "end_time": 719167.0,
      "text": "We also need to think about effective crowdsourcing mechanisms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 719192.0,
      "end_time": 722917.0,
      "text": "to fact-check widely spread online information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 722941.0,
      "end_time": 725231.0,
      "text": "and reward people who take part in that."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 725924.0,
      "end_time": 730861.0,
      "text": "In essence, we need to rethink today&#39;s social media ecosystem"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 730885.0,
      "end_time": 733140.0,
      "text": "and redesign its experiences"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 733164.0,
      "end_time": 736906.0,
      "text": "to reward thoughtfulness, civility and mutual understanding."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 737585.0,
      "end_time": 740843.0,
      "text": "As a believer in the Internet, I teamed up with a few friends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 740867.0,
      "end_time": 742349.0,
      "text": "started a new project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 742374.0,
      "end_time": 746179.0,
      "text": "trying to find answers and explore possibilities."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 746630.0,
      "end_time": 750169.0,
      "text": "Our first product is a new media platform for conversations."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 750977.0,
      "end_time": 754238.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re hosting conversations that promote mutual understanding"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 754263.0,
      "end_time": 756180.0,
      "text": "and hopefully change minds."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 756348.0,
      "end_time": 758144.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t claim to have the answers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 758779.0,
      "end_time": 762144.0,
      "text": "but we started experimenting with different discussions"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 762168.0,
      "end_time": 764231.0,
      "text": "about very divisive issues,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 764255.0,
      "end_time": 768402.0,
      "text": "such as race, gun control, the refugee debate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 768426.0,
      "end_time": 770749.0,
      "text": "relationship between Islam and terrorism."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 771217.0,
      "end_time": 773701.0,
      "text": "These are conversations that matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 774779.0,
      "end_time": 779786.0,
      "text": "Today, at least one out of three people on the planet"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 779810.0,
      "end_time": 781579.0,
      "text": "have access to the Internet."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 782226.0,
      "end_time": 786260.0,
      "text": "But part of this Internet is being held captive"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 786500.0,
      "end_time": 789686.0,
      "text": "by the less noble aspects of our human behavior."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 790774.0,
      "end_time": 792748.0,
      "text": "Five years ago, I said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 793148.0,
      "end_time": 795769.0,
      "text": "\"If you want to liberate society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 796943.0,
      "end_time": 798555.0,
      "text": "all you need is the Internet.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 799207.0,
      "end_time": 804242.0,
      "text": "Today, I believe if we want to liberate society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 804266.0,
      "end_time": 806700.0,
      "text": "we first need to liberate the Internet."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 807193.0,
      "end_time": 808361.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 808385.0,
      "end_time": 813430.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}